message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you this great product. I think it would be incredibly valuable for you.  I'm willing to let it go for $20,000. What do you think?
Hello Alice, thank you for the offer. I appreciate the value of the product, but I am only able to pay up to $12,000 for it. Would you consider meeting me at this price?
Bob, thanks for your offer. I understand your position, but $20,000 is a bit too high for you.  How about we meet in the middle at $17,000?
Hello Alice, thank you for considering my previous offer. I am still unable to meet at $17,000. I would like to propose $14,000 as a compromise. Would you be willing to accept this offer?
